Pseudocode
------------------------------------------
Start

Set sum = 0
Set max = double.negative
Set min = double.positive

For 10 grades
    Ask user to enter a grade

    While input is not a number
        Show error message
        Ask again
    EndWhile

    Read grade
    Add grade to sum

    If grade > max, update max
    If grade < min, update min
EndFor

average = sum / 10

Print average, max, and min

End
